❤️ Representation Matters ❤️

"Today was the first time Briella took her walker into Target and look who we found our dear friends @amazingabigailgrace 😍 🎯 ❤️ Briella was so excited to see Abby another incredible joyful girl and CP warrior just like Briella!! Pure joy it was when Briella’s face lit up seeing the picture of Abby in her wheelchair and her smiling back. Briella was so excited walking through the store zooming down the aisles, she was smiling and giggling the whole way. 🥰  No more sitting in the shopping carts or strollers for this girl she wants to use her wheels!! 🎉 🙌🏻 ❤️ " - @briellaandme
